      "text": [
        ": كيف بكم إذا صعدتم فلم تجدوا أحداً، ورجعتم فلم تجدوا أحداً!"
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(4) Bin Sinan narrated from Yahya bin al-Muthanna al-Attar, also it was narrated by al-Hakam that Abu Ja’far al-Baqir (as) had said: “How about you if you go and you do not find anyone (to resort to) and you come back and you do not find anyone?”"
        ]
